<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Meritorious" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Meritorious,</orth> deserving honour or reward: <cit><quote>'tis a m. fair design,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1692" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1692</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>m. service,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.2.217" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 2, 217</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>m. shall that hand be called,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 3.1.176" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 1, 176</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the deed is m.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.270" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 270</bibl></cit>.
